high_descs: Move to the coffee table in front of the couch closest to the door
Pick up tea kettle from the coffee table
Move the the display shelf directly ahead of the door to the left of the coffee table
Place kettle on the shelf
Move back to the same coffee table in front of the couch
Pick up second kettle off of the coffee table
Move to the same display shelf as before
Place kettle on to the display shelf
anns.task_desc: Move the tea kettles from the coffee table to the display shelf.

high_descs: Go straight to the chair. Turn left at the chair. Go in between the couch and the coffee table, face the coffee table.
Take the pot next to the remote control on the coffee table.
Turn left then go straight, turn right at the chair, go straight to the platform with the white plate.
Put the pot to the left of the white plate on the platform.
Turn around, Go straight to the chair. Turn left at the chair. Go in between the couch and the coffee table, face the coffee table.
Take the pot on the coffee table.
Turn left then go straight, turn right at the chair, go straight to the platform with the white plate.
Put the pot on the right side of the platform.
Begin walking across the room, then hang a left and walk over to the side of the coffee table that the watering can is on.
Pick up the closest white watering can off of the coffee table.
Turn left and begin walking over to the wall, then hang a right and walk up to the bench with a plate on it.
Place the watering can on the bench to the right of the plate.
Turn around and walk back to the coffee table.
Pick up the watering can off of the coffee table.
Turn left and walk across the room, then hang a right and walk up to the bench.
Place the watering can on the right side of the bench
anns.task_desc: Move to watering cans onto the bench.
